ca,sans-serif;\">Phiếu giảm giá: 5% / Hóa đơn mua xe; 20% / Hóa đơn mua phụ kiện</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #0000cd;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Gói Quà Tặng trị giá 700.000 đồng</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #0000cd;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">- Đèn Pin phượt 4 chế độ</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #0000cd;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">- Đèn chớp sau</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #0000cd;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">- Đồng hồ tốc độ 7 chế độ</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #0000cd;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">- Giá treo bình nước</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #0000cd;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">- Đèn cảm biến van xe</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #0000cd;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">- Chuông báo hiệu</span></span></span></p>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'xe-dap-the-thao-chevrolet-khong-yen-giam-soc', '', '', '2016-03-12 16:35:52', '2016-03-12 16:35:52', '', 0, 'http://xediennhat.vn/?post_type=product&#038;p=4644', 0, 'product', '', 0);
